<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator.FilterDevicesOfType" Title="FilterDevicesOfType method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator">IGraphicsDeviceEnumerator</PageRef> ->
    FilterDevicesOfType
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>FilterDevicesOfType</TypeRef> method removes all <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice">IGraphicsDevice</PageRef>
      objects from the current filtered device set, which have a <PageRef PageName="cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.DeviceType">DeviceType</PageRef>
      that matches the specified device type.
    </Paragraph>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void FilterDevicesOfType(IGraphicsDevice::DeviceType type);]]></Code>
    <SubSection Title="Argument list">
      <ArgumentList>
        <ArgumentListEntry Type="DeviceType!cobalt.graphics.IGraphicsDevice.DeviceType" Name="type">
          The type of devices you want to remove from the filtered device set
        </ArgumentListEntry>
      </ArgumentList>
    </SubSection>
  </Section>
